-- Wawrinka Upsets Ferrer in Portugal Open Tennis; Haas Victory
-- B y   P e t e r - J o s e p h   H e g a r t y
-- 2013-05-05T16:09:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-05/wawrinka-upsets-ferrer-in-portugal-open-tennis-haas-victory.html
Stanislas Wawrinka of Switzerland
upset Spain’s David Ferrer in straight sets in the final of
tennis’s ATP Portugal Open.  Second-seeded Wawrinka defeated top seed Ferrer 6-1, 6-4 in
Oeiras.  Tommy Haas  beat his German compatriot Philipp Kohlschreiber
in straight sets to win the ATP BMW Open. Third-seeded Haas
defeated the No. 4 seed 6-3, 7-6 (7-3) in Munich.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter-Joseph Hegarty at 
 phegarty@bloomberg.net  